00:37:15,266 --> 00:37:17,435
and when it mixed with the beef juice,

965
00:37:17,501 --> 00:37:18,469
it made the flavor so…

966
00:37:18,536 --> 00:37:19,637
Wow, it's just…

967
00:37:19,704 --> 00:37:22,440
The balance was perfect.

968
00:37:22,506 --> 00:37:24,909
Also, the enoki bottom.

969
00:37:24,976 --> 00:37:26,043
I adore the texture.

970
