978
00:37:46,797 --> 00:37:51,302
-The crunchiness was so good.
-I see.

979
00:37:51,369 --> 00:37:54,171
I did my job, so l let me continue.

980
00:37:55,039 --> 00:37:56,107
Yes, you can eat some more.

981
00:37:56,173 --> 00:37:58,075
May I try just one?

982
00:37:58,142 --> 00:37:59,677
-Just this one.
-There are more over there.

983
00:37:59,744 --> 00:38:01,379
