992
00:38:22,767 --> 00:38:24,935
THE MORE I EAT IT,
THE MORE DELICIOUS IT IS

993
00:38:25,002 --> 00:38:27,705
The juice from the meat
and the bell peppers will flow out

994
00:38:27,772 --> 00:38:29,073
