995
00:38:29,140 --> 00:38:30,207
You're on another level.

996
00:38:30,274 --> 00:38:32,943
-He finished second in the regular league.
-He delivered.

997
00:38:33,511 --> 00:38:36,213
WOW, SEXY ENOKI

998
00:38:36,447 --> 00:38:38,382
PLEASE STOP NOW…

999
00:38:38,449 --> 00:38:40,217
She's feeling it a bit too hard.

1000
00:38:40,284 --> 00:38:42,687
-I've seen that face somewhere.
-It's like an ad.

1001
00:38:43,187 --> 00:38:44,955
-It's so good.
-"It's so good."

1002
00:38:45,022 --> 00:38:47,224
