1009
00:39:06,777 --> 00:39:08,946
May I try this first?

1010
00:39:09,013 --> 00:39:11,515
-I'll try just the veggies.
-Just the veggies.

1011
00:39:11,582 --> 00:39:14,485
-She loves meat, but veggies too.
-And the apple.

1012
00:39:14,552 --> 00:39:15,486
