1015
00:39:23,594 --> 00:39:25,062
An actress's routine.

1016
00:39:25,996 --> 00:39:28,632
-I'll remove my toxins now.
-Okay.

1017
00:39:29,066 --> 00:39:30,368
YUM

1018
00:39:30,434 --> 00:39:32,136
It's her refreshing morning routine.

1019
00:39:32,203 --> 00:39:33,571
