1023
00:39:41,445 --> 00:39:45,282
-<i>Yes, peanut butter and balsamic vinegar.</i>
-<i>Peanut and balsamic.</i>

1024
00:39:46,183 --> 00:39:47,017
What is it?

1025
00:39:48,252 --> 00:39:49,520
-What do you want to say?
-She's nodding.

1026
00:39:49,587 --> 00:39:50,554
You aren't mad, are you?

1027
00:39:50,621 --> 00:39:52,823
