-You didn't even chew!

1044
00:40:33,097 --> 00:40:34,765
FALSELY ACCUSED

1045
00:40:34,832 --> 00:40:38,002
-You didn't chew.
-Your mouth didn't even move.

1046
00:40:38,068 --> 00:40:40,271
No, you can feel it
