-It's about time you win first place.

1184
00:46:07,297 --> 00:46:08,899
-She's amazing.
-It's about time.

1185
00:46:08,966 --> 00:46:13,103
<i>This is the second round played</i>
<i>with ingredients from Su-ji's fridge.</i>

1186
00:46:13,170 --> 00:46:16,707
<i>The 2025</i> Chef & My Fridge <i>Championship.</i>

1187
00:46:16,774 --> 00:46:19,977
